mages-for-Lionsgate.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">西里安·墨菲（Cillian Murphy）</a>领导了<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><i>高峰盲人</i></a>服装设计师斯蒂芬·科利（Stephanie Collie）的致敬，后者享年60岁。</p><p>这位演员与许多其他人致敬的人一起，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">瑞安·雷诺兹（Ryan Reynolds）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-craig">丹尼尔·克雷格（Daniel Craig）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">塞缪尔·杰克逊（Samuel L. Jackson）</a> ，他们都与著名的服装设计师合作。</p><p>该消息是通过官方的<i>Peaky Blinders</i> BBC Instagram帐户与粉丝分享的，并表彰了科利的“鼓舞人心”的作品。</p><p>声明中写道：“得知服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·科利去世的消息，我们感到非常悲伤。</p><p> “斯蒂芬妮（Stephanie）在我们的第一个系列中的令人难以置信的作品是创造<i>Peaky Blinders</i>的标志性外观的关键，并继续激发世界各地的许多人。</p><p> “我们的爱和思念与她的家人同在。”</p><p>墨菲（Murphy）在演出中扮演汤米·谢尔比（Tommy Shelby） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tommy-shelby-returns-in-peaky-blinders-movie-first-look-image-3798419#:~:text=Production%20has%20begun%20on%20Netflix,Cillian%20Murphy%20as%20Tommy%20Shelby.&amp;text=The%20film%20was%20first%20confirmed,Tom%20Harper%20set%20to%20direct.">，目前正在拍摄新的衍生电影</a>，他对科利（Collie）分享了自己的情感致敬。</p><p>他在一份声明中写道：“斯蒂芬妮是一个凶猛的才华。她发明的<i>《浴血黑帮》的</i>外观和轮廓已成为全世界的标志。</p><p> “我们都会想念她的。安息吧。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCjlnvHs0qX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886